    <span class="b">温馨提示：</span>您购买的投资宝将于<span class="red"><%= @current_user.mn_service_time %>天</span>后(<%= @current_user.mn_account.service_end_at.strftime("%Y年%m月%d日") %>)到期。<%= link_to "[立刻续费]".html_safe, new_premium_mobile_newspaper_account_url %>   
